item.title: Help?
item.dc:creator: @Riley Riley
item.description:
@Riley wrote:

On some servers, you can type ::barrows or, ::dragon. But some servers don’t allow that and it won’t work. So if it dosen’t you can easily type ::smithgold and make guilded kitesheilds, then sell them to the general store and buy Barrows, or dragon from the other people on that server, or from the shops if they have them. And another way is to buy a dramen staff from the guy who sells staffs in varrock, Then type in ::teletobarrows and click on the door, open the chest, and get barrows. Be careful not to click so fast, it will lagg the server.
